"this" Keyword:
      -> This is used to refer the current class object.
      -> "this" is used inside a method or a constructor.

Usages of this keyword:
      ->  This used to refer current class instance variable. To overcome the variable hiding we use this keyword.
      -> invoke current class method
           we can invoke a current class method using this keyword from anothter method in the same class.
      -> "this()" is used to invoke current class constructor.
      -> 'this' can be passed as argument in the method call.
      -> 'this' can be passed as argument in the constructor call.
      -> this can be used to return current class instance.



